Package net.metarelate.terminology.publisher.templateElements Description

Template elements used by the template manager. Template elements implement a few interfaces that are meant to represent templates that never change, that change for each code, or that present parameters depending on the terminology as a whole. However, this interface approach is badly designed, as effectively only a few methods are called, with null values are not relevant for the specific case.
